> say that the SmartMedia is fine, but the FlashPath is a 
> little silly. (And I sometimes feel very bad for what
> I was forced to write due to NDA and time constraints)..
A lot of the NDA's on smart media are the smart media peoples problem more
than the interface card vendors. The simple answer is to use compact flash
which has a published hardware interface and you don't have to sign up for
deeply magical pieces of paper to talk to
